title: Connection Checker - Java 6 Version (reup)
description:
This neat little program checks our internet connection and informs you when its status changes from connected to disconnected. This usually happens before programs like ICQ detect the status change which can be extremely useful in unstable wifi environments. It also helps to keep track of how stable your connection really is because some programs miss short disconnects completely.

Required: Java 1.6
Get it from http://www.java.com
